{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":719,"text":"I'd like to talk today"},{"time":2209,"text":"about a powerful and fundamental aspect"},{"time":5136,"text":"of who we are: our voice."},{"time":8734,"text":"Each one of us has a unique voiceprint"},{"time":11480,"text":"that reflects our age, our size,"},{"time":13769,"text":"even our lifestyle and personality."},{"time":17006,"text":"In the words of the poet Longfellow,"},{"time":19148,"text":"\"the human voice is the organ of the soul.\""},{"time":23018,"text":"As a speech scientist, I'm fascinated"},{"time":25765,"text":"by how the voice is produced,"},{"time":27594,"text":"and I have an idea for how it can be engineered."},{"time":31252,"text":"That's what I'd like to share with you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33462,"text":"I'm going to start by playing you a sample"},{"time":35276,"text":"of a voice that you may recognize."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37147,"text":"(Recording) Stephen Hawking: \"I would have thought"},{"time":38451,"text":"it was fairly obvious what I meant.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":41200,"text":"Rupal Patel: That was the voice"},{"time":42480,"text":"of Professor Stephen Hawking."},{"time":44566,"text":"What you may not know is that same voice"},{"time":48415,"text":"may also be used by this little girl"},{"time":50893,"text":"who is unable to speak"},{"time":52590,"text":"because of a neurological condition."},{"time":55187,"text":"In fact, all of these individuals"},{"time":57255,"text":"may be using the same voice,"},{"time":59267,"text":"and that's because there's\nonly a few options available."},{"time":62824,"text":"In the U.S. alone, there are 2.5 million Americans"},{"time":67141,"text":"who are unable to speak,"},{"time":68751,"text":"and many of whom use computerized devices"},{"time":71373,"text":"to communicate."},{"time":72895,"text":"Now that's millions of people worldwide"},{"time":76374,"text":"who are using generic voices,"},{"time":78026,"text":"including Professor Hawking,"},{"time":79472,"text":"who uses an American-accented voice."},{"time":84305,"text":"This lack of individuation of the synthetic voice"},{"time":87633,"text":"really hit home"},{"time":89049,"text":"when I was at an assistive technology conference"},{"time":91521,"text":"a few years ago,"},{"time":93371,"text":"and I recall walking into an exhibit hall"},{"time":96975,"text":"and seeing a little girl and a grown man"},{"time":100019,"text":"having a conversation using their devices,"},{"time":102935,"text":"different devices, but the same voice."},{"time":107219,"text":"And I looked around and I saw this happening"},{"time":109128,"text":"all around me, literally hundreds of individuals"},{"time":113318,"text":"using a handful of voices,"},{"time":116056,"text":"voices that didn't fit their bodies"},{"time":119147,"text":"or their personalities."},{"time":121229,"text":"We wouldn't dream of fitting a little girl"},{"time":123956,"text":"with the prosthetic limb of a grown man."},{"time":127352,"text":"So why then the same prosthetic voice?"},{"time":130656,"text":"It really struck me,"},{"time":131947,"text":"and I wanted to do something about this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135098,"text":"I'm going to play you now a sample"},{"time":137051,"text":"of someone who has, two people actually,"},{"time":140339,"text":"who have severe speech disorders."},{"time":142107,"text":"I want you to take a listen to how they sound."},{"time":145337,"text":"They're saying the same utterance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147694,"text":"(First voice)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":150126,"text":"(Second voice)"},{"time":153743,"text":"You probably didn't understand what they said,"},{"time":156155,"text":"but I hope that you heard"},{"time":158009,"text":"their unique vocal identities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162292,"text":"So what I wanted to do next is,"},{"time":165105,"text":"I wanted to find out how we could harness"},{"time":167489,"text":"these residual vocal abilities"},{"time":169310,"text":"and build a technology"},{"time":171326,"text":"that could be customized for them,"},{"time":173469,"text":"voices that could be customized for them."},{"time":175898,"text":"So I reached out to my collaborator, Tim Bunnell."},{"time":178583,"text":"Dr. Bunnell is an expert in speech synthesis,"},{"time":181646,"text":"and what he'd been doing is building"},{"time":183679,"text":"personalized voices for people"},{"time":185560,"text":"by putting together"},{"time":187657,"text":"pre-recorded samples of their voice"},{"time":189807,"text":"and reconstructing a voice for them."},{"time":192686,"text":"These are people who had lost their voice"},{"time":194398,"text":"later in life."},{"time":196309,"text":"We didn't have the luxury"},{"time":197703,"text":"of pre-recorded samples of speech"},{"time":199477,"text":"for those born with speech disorder."},{"time":201769,"text":"But I thought, there had to be a way"},{"time":204306,"text":"to reverse engineer a voice"},{"time":206250,"text":"from whatever little is left over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208541,"text":"So we decided to do exactly that."},{"time":211255,"text":"We set out with a little bit of funding\nfrom the National Science Foundation,"},{"time":214658,"text":"to create custom-crafted voices that captured"},{"time":218223,"text":"their unique vocal identities."},{"time":219759,"text":"We call this project VocaliD, or vocal I.D.,"},{"time":222962,"text":"for vocal identity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224995,"text":"Now before I get into the details of how"},{"time":227669,"text":"the voice is made and let you listen to it,"},{"time":229717,"text":"I need to give you a real quick\nspeech science lesson. Okay?"},{"time":233067,"text":"So first, we know that the voice is changing"},{"time":236226,"text":"dramatically over the course of development."},{"time":239080,"text":"Children sound different from teens"},{"time":241170,"text":"who sound different from adults."},{"time":242633,"text":"We've all experienced this."},{"time":245275,"text":"Fact number two is that speech"},{"time":248638,"text":"is a combination of the source,"},{"time":251191,"text":"which is the vibrations generated by your voice box,"},{"time":254670,"text":"which are then pushed through"},{"time":256609,"text":"the rest of the vocal tract."},{"time":259046,"text":"These are the chambers of your head and neck"},{"time":261530,"text":"that vibrate,"},{"time":262769,"text":"and they actually filter that source sound"},{"time":264879,"text":"to produce consonants and vowels."},{"time":267416,"text":"So the combination of source and filter"},{"time":271276,"text":"is how we produce speech."},{"time":273906,"text":"And that happens in one individual."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276932,"text":"Now I told you earlier that I'd spent"},{"time":279558,"text":"a good part of my career"},{"time":281583,"text":"understanding and studying"},{"time":284036,"text":"the source characteristics of people"},{"time":285994,"text":"with severe speech disorder,"},{"time":288295,"text":"and what I've found"},{"time":289760,"text":"is that even though their filters were impaired,"},{"time":293126,"text":"they were able to modulate their source:"},{"time":296087,"text":"the pitch, the loudness, the tempo of their voice."},{"time":299349,"text":"These are called prosody, and\nI've been documenting for years"},{"time":302717,"text":"that the prosodic abilities of these individuals"},{"time":304994,"text":"are preserved."},{"time":306569,"text":"So when I realized that those same cues"},{"time":310656,"text":"are also important for speaker identity,"},{"time":313425,"text":"I had this idea."},{"time":315440,"text":"Why don't we take the source"},{"time":317956,"text":"from the person we want the voice to sound like,"},{"time":320169,"text":"because it's preserved,"},{"time":321632,"text":"and borrow the filter"},{"time":323767,"text":"from someone about the same age and size,"},{"time":327011,"text":"because they can articulate speech,"},{"time":329418,"text":"and then mix them?"},{"time":331209,"text":"Because when we mix them,"},{"time":332996,"text":"we can get a voice that's as clear"},{"time":334694,"text":"as our surrogate talker --"},{"time":336448,"text":"that's the person we borrowed the filter fromâ€”"},{"time":339043,"text":"and is similar in identity to our target talker."},{"time":343692,"text":"It's that simple."},{"time":345119,"text":"That's the science behind what we're doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348053,"text":"So once you have that in mind,"},{"time":351586,"text":"how do you go about building this voice?"},{"time":353844,"text":"Well, you have to find someone"},{"time":355324,"text":"who is willing to be a surrogate."},{"time":357724,"text":"It's not such an ominous thing."},{"time":359988,"text":"Being a surrogate donor"},{"time":361511,"text":"only requires you to say a few hundred"},{"time":364299,"text":"to a few thousand utterances."},{"time":366541,"text":"The process goes something like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368544,"text":"(Video) Voice: Things happen in pairs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370734,"text":"I love to sleep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372659,"text":"The sky is blue without clouds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376541,"text":"RP: Now she's going to go on like this"},{"time":378543,"text":"for about three to four hours,"},{"time":380462,"text":"and the idea is not for her to say everything"},{"time":383467,"text":"that the target is going to want to say,"},{"time":385512,"text":"but the idea is to cover all the different combinations"},{"time":388907,"text":"of the sounds that occur in the language."},{"time":392178,"text":"The more speech you have,"},{"time":393816,"text":"the better sounding voice you're going to have."},{"time":396121,"text":"Once you have those recordings,"},{"time":397794,"text":"what we need to do"},{"time":399207,"text":"is we have to parse these recordings"},{"time":401925,"text":"into little snippets of speech,"},{"time":404374,"text":"one- or two-sound combinations,"},{"time":406711,"text":"sometimes even whole words"},{"time":408594,"text":"that start populating a dataset or a database."},{"time":413110,"text":"We're going to call this database a voice bank."},{"time":416827,"text":"Now the power of the voice bank"},{"time":418923,"text":"is that from this voice bank,"},{"time":420937,"text":"we can now say any new utterance,"},{"time":422948,"text":"like, \"I love chocolate\" --"},{"time":424372,"text":"everyone needs to be able to say thatâ€”"},{"time":426111,"text":"fish through that database"},{"time":427942,"text":"and find all the segments necessary"},{"time":429882,"text":"to say that utterance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431811,"text":"(Video) Voice: I love chocolate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433600,"text":"RP: So that's speech synthesis."},{"time":434991,"text":"It's called concatenative synthesis,\nand that's what we're using."},{"time":437564,"text":"That's not the novel part."},{"time":439097,"text":"What's novel is how we make it sound"},{"time":441318,"text":"like this young woman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442775,"text":"This is Samantha."},{"time":444299,"text":"I met her when she was nine,"},{"time":446645,"text":"and since then, my team and I"},{"time":448542,"text":"have been trying to build her a personalized voice."},{"time":451256,"text":"We first had to find a surrogate donor,"},{"time":454355,"text":"and then we had to have Samantha"},{"time":456173,"text":"produce some utterances."},{"time":458102,"text":"What she can produce are mostly vowel-like sounds,"},{"time":460481,"text":"but that's enough for us to extract"},{"time":462960,"text":"her source characteristics."},{"time":465245,"text":"What happens next is best described"},{"time":468516,"text":"by my daughter's analogy. She's six."},{"time":471283,"text":"She calls it mixing colors to paint voices."},{"time":476705,"text":"It's beautiful. It's exactly that."},{"time":479260,"text":"Samantha's voice is like a concentrated sample"},{"time":482120,"text":"of red food dye which we can infuse"},{"time":484729,"text":"into the recordings of her surrogate"},{"time":487269,"text":"to get a pink voice just like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491656,"text":"(Video) Samantha: Aaaaaah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496147,"text":"RP: So now, Samantha can say this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498955,"text":"(Video) Samantha: This voice is only for me."},{"time":502024,"text":"I can't wait to use my new voice with my friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508329,"text":"RP: Thank you. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":514746,"text":"I'll never forget the gentle smile"},{"time":517079,"text":"that spread across her face"},{"time":518981,"text":"when she heard that voice for the first time."},{"time":522630,"text":"Now there's millions of people"},{"time":524512,"text":"around the world like Samantha, millions,"},{"time":527345,"text":"and we've only begun to scratch the surface."},{"time":530785,"text":"What we've done so far is we have"},{"time":532427,"text":"a few surrogate talkers from around the U.S."},{"time":536286,"text":"who have donated their voices,"},{"time":537793,"text":"and we have been using those"},{"time":539721,"text":"to build our first few personalized voices."},{"time":544193,"text":"But there's so much more work to be done."},{"time":545949,"text":"For Samantha, her surrogate"},{"time":548137,"text":"came from somewhere in the Midwest, a stranger"},{"time":551183,"text":"who gave her the gift of voice."},{"time":555024,"text":"And as a scientist, I'm so excited"},{"time":557177,"text":"to take this work out of the laboratory"},{"time":559112,"text":"and finally into the real world"},{"time":560912,"text":"so it can have real-world impact."},{"time":564077,"text":"What I want to share with you next"},{"time":565659,"text":"is how I envision taking this work"},{"time":567834,"text":"to that next level."},{"time":570545,"text":"I imagine a whole world of surrogate donors"},{"time":574432,"text":"from all walks of life, different sizes, different ages,"},{"time":577692,"text":"coming together in this voice drive"},{"time":580750,"text":"to give people voices"},{"time":583020,"text":"that are as colorful as their personalities."},{"time":586819,"text":"To do that as a first step,"},{"time":589119,"text":"we've put together this website, VocaliD.org,"},{"time":592394,"text":"as a way to bring together those"},{"time":594018,"text":"who want to join us as voice donors,"},{"time":596693,"text":"as expertise donors,"},{"time":598465,"text":"in whatever way to make this vision a reality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603804,"text":"They say that giving blood can save lives."},{"time":607957,"text":"Well, giving your voice can change lives."},{"time":612939,"text":"All we need is a few hours of speech"},{"time":615989,"text":"from our surrogate talker,"},{"time":617480,"text":"and as little as a vowel from our target talker,"},{"time":622213,"text":"to create a unique vocal identity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625924,"text":"So that's the science behind what we're doing."},{"time":628550,"text":"I want to end by circling back to the human side"},{"time":633005,"text":"that is really the inspiration for this work."},{"time":637107,"text":"About five years ago, we built our very first voice"},{"time":640806,"text":"for a little boy named William."},{"time":643307,"text":"When his mom first heard this voice,"},{"time":645664,"text":"she said, \"This is what William"},{"time":648009,"text":"would have sounded like"},{"time":649555,"text":"had he been able to speak.\""},{"time":652004,"text":"And then I saw William typing a message"},{"time":654422,"text":"on his device."},{"time":655784,"text":"I wondered, what was he thinking?"},{"time":659077,"text":"Imagine carrying around someone else's voice"},{"time":662667,"text":"for nine years"},{"time":664860,"text":"and finally finding your own voice."},{"time":669704,"text":"Imagine that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671081,"text":"This is what William said:"},{"time":673878,"text":"\"Never heard me before.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":680417,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":682036,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}